               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18421128-name-1410" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-1410" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-1410" type="surname" value="PERRY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-1410" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PERRY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a brewer, and live in St. George's-road, Southwark. This is my sachrometer—I saw it safe on Monday the 21st of Nov., and it was missed on the Monday following—the prisoner had been in my service, but was discharged on the 11th of June last.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Have you a great many other servants? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—he was discharged for drunkenness—I had no charge against him for dishonesty.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18421128-name-1411" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-1411" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-1411" type="surname" value="HAZLEBY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-1411" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN HAZLEBY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker. I took in this sachrometer of the prisoner, on the 25th of Nov., about six o'clock in the evening.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Did you know him before? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Not to my know<lb></lb>ledge—my masters's shop is in the Lower-road; Deptford—that is rather a populous neighbourhood—it was candle light—there were other customers in the shop, but I do not know that I should know any of them again—I was the only person serving.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">COURT</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Are you sure he is the man that pawned this? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Quite sure.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
